The real part is \(9.0\).

The imaginary part is \(-7.0i + (-4.00i) = -11.0i\).

Thus, the sum of the complex numbers is \(9.0 - 11.0i\).

The final answer is:

\[
\text{<<<9.0 - 11.0i>>>}
